{"tid":2283233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上年11月12日你仲記唔記得發生咩事","createTime":"2020-11-12T11:52:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T01:45:23.000Z","uid":129068,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e1a5517ba14d75b7b3324fec1c7a698bfcbc3847","tid":2283233,"uid":129068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T11:52:02.000Z","msg":"中文大學變成了一座烽火台。<br />\n<br />\n是不是整座大學，變成了林鄭月娥眼中的暴亂基地？<br />\n<br />\n三百年前，雍正皇帝也派清兵攻打並火燒少林寺，因為少林寺被認定窩藏叛亂的反清志士。<br />\n<br />\n當年英國殖民地政府，見民國知識分子錢穆等人，逃亡香港，保存宣揚在大陸成為灰燼的中國儒家文化，於心不忍，將這一角山水，建設成中文大學。<br />\n<br />\n今日，香港和海外的中大校友，不知作何感想？<br />\n<br />\n中國人的歷史悲劇，在這籠黑煙之中，見盡其宿命循環。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hOkKWrt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhOkKWrt.png&h=0c74d6e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bDSxkTd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbDSxkTd.jpg&h=18257e97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/272574169481780/posts/3172138529525315/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F272574169481780%2Fposts%2F3172138529525315%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2BytmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=0c9a2ff7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/272574169481780/posts/3172138529525315/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"be5c06b7b33b227ec5ef4a520c236b2159c034e1","tid":2283233,"uid":129068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T11:53:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"812da458d38ed15b1ed8db38686c0d942436e4e2","tid":2283233,"uid":129068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T11:54:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cGePn7U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcGePn7U.jpg&h=350b2b9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"422fea639695315e1c12719f06be70dab6bc7266","tid":2283233,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:03:55.000Z","msg":"<